{"word":"G423 - ἀνεπίληπτος - anepílēptos - an-ep-eel'-ape-tos - Blameless","slug":"G423","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνεπίληπτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>anepílēptos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>an-ep-eel'-ape-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Blameless"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - anepile&#x0304;ptos</b> - <i>an-ep-eel'-ape-tos</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1949\">G1949</a>; <i>not arrested</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>inculpable:</i> - blameless, unrebukeable."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274\">G5274</a>"}]}